headline: Why Fortive (FTV) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of industrial technology company Fortive (NYSE:FTV) jumped 3.3% in the afternoon session after the company presented a confident strategic outlook at Morgan Stanley's 13th Annual Laguna Conference.
